    <string name="tour_notif_title">A word about the ongoing notification 🔔</string>
    <string name="tour_notif_body">You may notice a persistent notification in your status bar. This keeps the real-time connection alive so you receive messages, visits, and events instantly — even when the app is in the background.

Without it, Android would put the service to sleep and you would miss notifications. It is low-priority and silent, so it will never buzz you.</string>

    <string name="tour_step1_title">Welcome to JALNotifier 👋</string>
    <string name="tour_step1_body">Stay connected to JALF — your messages, events, and contacts are all in one place. Navigate between tabs using the bar below.</string>
    <string name="tour_step1_body_tablet">Stay connected to JALF — your messages, events, and contacts are all in one place. Navigate between tabs using the sidebar on the left.</string>

    <string name="tour_step2_title">Your Profile</string>
    <string name="tour_step2_body">Tap your avatar to see your profile details, toggle status, and access settings.</string>

    <string name="tour_step3_title">Events &amp; Visits</string>
    <string name="tour_step3_body">See who viewed your profile, liked your photo, or sent you a greeting — all in real time on the Events tab.</string>

    <string name="tour_step4_title">Notification Settings</string>
    <string name="tour_step4_body">Tap Settings in this profile sheet to customize your notification preferences (filtering by sex and contact types).</string>

    <string name="tour_step5_title">Filter by Sex &amp; Contact Type 🔔</string>
    <string name="tour_step5_body">In Notifications → By Sexes: choose which genders can notify you for each event type.\n\nIn Notifications → By Contact Types: get alerts only for your Favorites, Bookmarks, or Followed Users — per event type (Messages, Visits, Pokes, Favorites, Photos).</string>

    <string name="tour_step6_title">Auto Ghost Mode 👻</string>
    <string name="tour_step6_body">Go to Settings → Security &amp; Biometrics → Auto Appear Offline. Set a timer (5 min, 15 min, 30 min, or up to 12 hours). JALNotifier will automatically switch you to Ghost Mode after that period of inactivity — and restore your presence when you return.</string>

    <string name="tour_step7_title">Quick Responses ⚡</string>
    <string name="tour_step7_body">Create custom message templates in Settings under the Quick Responses section. When chatting, swipe a template to send it instantly or long-press to edit it, saving you time when replying on the go.</string>

    <string name="tour_chat_title">Messages &amp; Chats</string>
    <string name="tour_chat_body">View and respond to all your JALF messages in real time.</string>

    <string name="tour_search_title">Unified Search</string>
    <string name="tour_search_body">Find members easily using filters for age, location, status, and physical characteristics.</string>

    <string name="tour_contacts_title">Favorites, Bookmarks &amp; Followed</string>
    <string name="tour_contacts_body">Keep track of your Favorites, Bookmarks, and Followed contacts in one list.</string>

